:49:01.000Z","msg":"司法公義同執法公義同立法不義，後兩者香港不嬲無，前者都一直受限受釋法打壓"},{"pid":"6a0e658383a7ad4dcf8869e194c1182812c4159d","tid":1809731,"uid":5216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T10:49:15.000Z","msg":"反共<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n槍仇必報<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n612 721 811 831 929 101 112 113 1111 1112 1117 1118 新屋嶺 還眼 還命 被自殺 實彈 周同學 雞姦 強姦 輪姦 因姦成孕 圍攻大學 人踩人 濫捕濫殺 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc403e2fd7bcae1fc877f90234963f2ab8c911b7","tid":1809731,"uid":163149,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6f2595dba864b1a13cfc00008953ec16ee659d46","tid":1809731,"uid":225130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"236a6620b602002a9f20ca90fbeab98a63d7a9fb","tid":1809731,"uid":41998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"198d1b419fb064762fedc7b55fc9e862be110041","tid":1809731,"uid":225130,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T10:39:27.000Z","msg":"屯門個細路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n要更生中心 屌"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T10:44:31.000Z","msg":"冇上訴？<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n冇記錯，佢係鐳射筆同話改裝遮？<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T10:45:41.000Z","msg":"上訴保釋好似唔成功"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T10:50:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20191125/6YAZVTO76BZL5UCK66DXUNJIOU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20191125%2F6YAZVTO76BZL5UCK66DXUNJIOU%2F&d=GDp31xM3xvXFOTrKf8Ol7Gvf1q1qK4rBaJpe4ZKN2Es%3D&h=b4cd2242\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20191125%2F6YAZVTO76BZL5UCK66DXUNJIOU%2F&h=6ccce4d5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20191125/6YAZVTO76BZL5UCK66DXUNJIOU/</a><br />\n<br />\n連同涉及改裝遮及行山杖、按《公安條例》檢控的「在公眾地方管有攻擊性武器」罪，法庭隨即宣判少年兩罪罪成。<span style=\"color: red;\">裁判官當時指出，雷射筆本身並非武器，但若攜帶意圖是用來傷人，便符合武器定義。</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n法治？ 得啖笑， 個官話你有意圖你就係有意圖"},{"pid":"1e3d46fb9664609fd7d0899bd276b0a2f8685a44","tid":1809731,"uid":263878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T10:52:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3a70ff5768250ccbe0360c35814da7c0f0164b8","tid":1809731,"uid":238214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3226c565eee652487af28828151cd310c6895f63","tid":1809731,"uid":63779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5637bcaa6b184a9d961e3c00022a22915a700729","tid":1809731,"uid":238214,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"d4ea544ac4c01b1171fa476d26714c19cfae0dd8","tid":1809731,"uid":283040,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T10:16:43.000Z","msg":"但遇到紅官就危險呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T10:17:54.000Z","msg":"都要跟案例去判"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T10:38:34.000Z","msg":"高院或以上先算係案例。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T10:53:11.000Z","msg":"遵循先例（Stare decisis）是指在普通法中，作為判例的先例對其後的案件具有法律約束力<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">，法院以後面對相同的問題時必須作出同樣判決的原則</span></span></strong>。遵循先例是判例法形成的基礎。[1]<br />\n<br />\n當然，法院也有上級和下級之分。高級法院的判決對下級法院處理同類案件有約束力，但高級法院卻可以推翻下級法院的先例。另外，如果產生某個案件先例的客觀條件有所改變，使這個先例變得不合理時，法院可以改變或者推翻先例"},{"pid":"1927d83cbb535caeb9c7cab03c82a9d1fed3a84c","tid":1809731,"uid":126731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T10:53:31.000Z","msg":"紅底官真破壞法治。"},{"pid":"03dc564d006e59b5d3099780dc6060e1df62440b","tid":1809731,"uid":57221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T10:58:50.000Z","msg":"p"},{"pid":"67f43c7cc4b205545aa0019c27c53cd521e116f1","tid":1809731,"uid":127675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T11:01:33.000Z","msg":"點解咁多無業比人拉架 有冇黃店請番手足?<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"848a4de6a899af912bf808107e57f12345bb3061","tid":1809731,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d9db2894b74a9beb93c62f25b8852f71ce47eb1f","tid":1809731,"uid":51271,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T10:24:52.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">辯方反駁指，「被告坐係到唔代表啲咩」，又指涉案士巴拿實屬手掌大的微型士巴拿，可用於砌模型等，斥律政司無理檢控。林官最終指，被告單純管有兩支士巴拿，不等於自招嫌疑，故批准其訟費申請。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢樣係重點"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T11:11:40.000Z","msg":"其實呢啲買家私付送嘅扳手幾方便<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2020/01/03/OCx0oU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2020%2F01%2F03%2FOCx0oU.png&h=29ad663d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f05ff85a2b3af6e44cd56585973ef90599112ada","tid":1809731,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"67f43c7cc4b205545aa0019c27c53cd521e116f1","tid":1809731,"uid":127675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T11:01:33.000Z","msg":"點解咁多無業比人拉架 有冇黃店請番手足?<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T11:12:49.000Z","msg":"我被拉都會報無業 , 廢事啲狗去公司大大聲扮調查"},{"pid":"389f5750850c271e155055b16ab333f443da713b","tid":1809731,"uid":163149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f05ff85a2b3af6e44cd56585973ef90599112ada","tid":1809731,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"67f43c7cc4b205545aa0019c27c53cd521e116f1","tid":1809731,"uid":127675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T11:01:33.000Z","msg":"點解咁多無業比人拉架 有冇黃店請番手足?<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T11:12:49.000Z","msg":"我被拉都會報無業 , 廢事啲狗去公司大大聲扮調查"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T11:13:56.000Z","msg":"係， 駛撚同佢講做咩職業， 你話同件案有關就話姐"},{"pid":"5d1d8c56cd8a36021823c3c0bed37aa4cd4b1abc","tid":1809731,"uid":63779,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"c3a70ff5768250ccbe0360c35814da7c0f0164b8","tid":1809731,"uid":238214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3226c565eee652487af28828151cd310c6895f63","tid":1809731,"uid":63779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5637bcaa6b184a9d961e3c00022a22915a700729","tid":1809731,"uid":238214,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T10:17:54.000Z","msg":"都要跟案例去判"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T10:38:34.000Z","msg":"高院或以上先算係案例。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T10:53:11.000Z","msg":"遵循先例（Stare decisis）是指在普通法中，作為判例的先例對其後的案件具有法律約束力<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">，法院以後面對相同的問題時必須作出同樣判決的原則</span></span></strong>。遵循先例是判例法形成的基礎。[1]<br />\n<br />\n當然，法院也有上級和下級之分。高級法院的判決對下級法院處理同類案件有約束力，但高級法院卻可以推翻下級法院的先例。另外，如果產生某個案件先例的客觀條件有所改變，使這個先例變得不合理時，法院可以改變或者推翻先例"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T11:14:23.000Z","msg":"裁判法院的判決，不會成為權威案例，下次有同類案件時，裁判官不需要根據之前的判決作裁決，只有在高等法院或以上級別法院的判決，才會按普通法成為案例。"},{"pid":"ee57a5c4a4c56f03a8d556e483414ba1ec81e504","tid":1809731,"uid":190579,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"c0c6957c6858676af2b19eb7a46843bd1d071682","tid":1809731,"uid":163149,"like":73,"dislike":1,"score":72,"quote":{"pid":"02eb8ce37ede2fdbf83467c92c661c67b870a839","tid":1809731,"uid":51985,"like":110,"dislike":2,"score":108,"citedBy":7,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T10:04:03.000Z","msg":"即係代表 之前拉嘅藏有工具作不法用途<br />\n根